AGI - Arrested by the finance guard Pisicchio and his brother, both at home. Alfonsino Pisicchio, leader of Civic Sense, who in the Emilian Junta was also a regional council member in the last legislature, had left his post today at the head of the Regional Agency for Technology and Innovation. Pisicchio had explained that at the end of the month he would try to participate in the call for the direction of the academy of Fine Arts and feared they were incompatible charges. The Regional Junta this morning appointed to the head of the Art, instead of Pisicchio, the extraordinary commissioner Cosimo Elefante, regional manager, RTD (responsible for the transition to digital) of the Puglia Region.
&nbsp;
The brothers Enzo and Alfonsino Pisicchio are disputed the crimes concerning the Bv Tech Spa affair for the obtainment of a financing from more than 19 million euros, granted on 2 August 2018, within the project "Suite Products Cyber Security and SOC" with the role of the agency Puglia Sviluppo Spa for the feasibility study of the project for admission to state aid. The BV Tech is a company operating in the field of integrated engineering design and is administered by Raffaele Boccardo (inquired and not subject to caution).
&nbsp;
In the investigation, which led to the precautionary measure of the domiciles for the two brothers, the alleged crimes are those of aggravated, false scam, as well as the crime of false invoicing for non-existent operations. According to what emerged from the ordinance a "anticipation of regional financing achieved on 11 November 2018 through the use of one of the false policies of Cosimo Napolitano (in prison, ndr)".
&nbsp;
The company speaks on the phone twice the Pisicchio brothers: Enzo reports to Alfonsino that "where he went to Rome for work, he would take the opportunity to talk to Boccardo, about the project in existence and for which the company Bv Tech had funding from the Puglia Region". The brothers would have manifested "their suspicion that society" had "used state aid without respecting the timing and realization of the project". The order reads: Alfonsino asked: "You go get those things." Expression, which for the pollutants, assumes a meaning "sense only if an existing relationship between Bv Tech and the Pisicchio family is hypothesized". &nbsp;

